1. *Ovoga* puta nisam uspela da se sastanem sa prijateljima. (This time I wasn't able to meet up with my friends.)
2. Učitelj nam je dao *ovog*a časa test. (The teacher gave us a test this time.)
3. Volim da provodim vreme *ovog*a leta. (I love spending my time this summer.)
4. On je kupio *ovog*a meseca novi automobil. (He bought a new car this month.)
5. Nisam imala vremena da uradim *ovog*a dana zadatke. (I didn't have time to do the tasks this day.)